      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MERCEDES DANGER (7) was well in the market last time but only managed sixth (19.85), beaten 4 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Worth another chance. PIECE OF ME (5) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (30.48) in a Grade 5 at Launceston. Has the ability and can find best this time. WHERE'S AUNTY (1) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 340m behind Fishing Yari (19.90) in a Grade 3/4. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. VISTA YANK (4) scored by 2 lengths last time (19.33) in a Grade 4 over 340m at this track. Has already won two times from this draw.",
